data.text:
The Stylistics

7:30PM, Wednesday, November 06, 2024

Venue: Darlington Hippodrome

GREATEST HITS TOUR THE STYLISTICS are known instantly for their many recognisable hits such as the Grammy nominated ‘You Make Me Feel Brand New’ plus numerous classics including ‘Can’t Give You Anything (But My Love), ‘Let’s Put it All together’, ‘Stop Look Listen’, ‘You are Everything’, ‘Betcha by Golly Wow’, ‘Sing Baby Sing’ and more. THE STYLISTICS remain the real deal, fabulously entertaining and musically breathtaking, plying audiences with the hits that made them a household name.
